**SyncService.cs** - background sync when online:
```csharp
using System.Net.Http.Json;
using SiteInspector.Client.Models;

namespace SiteInspector.Client.Services;

public class SyncService : IAsyncDisposable
{
    private readonly InspectionService _inspectionService;
    private readonly HttpClient _http;
    private readonly ILogger<SyncService> _logger;
    private Timer? _timer;

    public bool IsOnline { get; private set; } = true;
    public event Action? OnConnectivityChanged;
    public DateTime? LastSyncedAt { get; private set; }

    public SyncService(InspectionService inspectionService, HttpClient http, ILogger<SyncService> logger)
    {
        _inspectionService = inspectionService;
        _http = http;
        _logger = logger;
    }

    public void Start()
    {
        _timer = new Timer(async _ => await TrySyncAsync(), null, TimeSpan.FromSeconds(5), TimeSpan.FromSeconds(30));
    }

    public async Task TrySyncAsync()
    {
        try
        {
            // Check connectivity by hitting the sync endpoint
            var response = await _http.GetAsync("api/sync/ping");
            var wasOffline = !IsOnline;
            IsOnline = response.IsSuccessStatusCode;

            if (wasOffline && IsOnline)
                OnConnectivityChanged?.Invoke();

            if (!IsOnline) return;

            // Upload unsynced inspections
            var unsynced = await _inspectionService.GetUnsyncedInspectionsAsync();
            foreach (var inspection in unsynced)
            {
                try
                {
                    var syncResponse = await _http.PostAsJsonAsync("api/sync/inspections", inspection);
                    if (syncResponse.IsSuccessStatusCode)
                    {
                        inspection.IsSynced = true;
                        await _inspectionService.SaveInspectionAsync(inspection);
                    }
                }
                catch { /* individual failure, try next */ }
            }

            // Upload sites
            var sites = await _inspectionService.GetSitesAsync();
            foreach (var site in sites)
            {
                try { await _http.PostAsJsonAsync("api/sync/sites", site); }
                catch { /* best effort */ }
            }

            LastSyncedAt = DateTime.UtcNow;
            OnConnectivityChanged?.Invoke();
        }
        catch
        {
            if (IsOnline) { IsOnline = false; OnConnectivityChanged?.Invoke(); }
        }
    }

    public ValueTask DisposeAsync()
    {
        _timer?.Dispose();
        return ValueTask.CompletedTask;
    }
}
```

### 5. Pages (`SiteInspector.Client/Pages/`)

**Home.razor** - Dashboard showing sites and recent inspections, link to add site:
- Shows connectivity status indicator
- List of sites with inspection count
- Quick "New Inspection" button
- Last sync time

**Sites.razor** (`/sites`) - Manage construction sites:
- Add new site form (name, address)
- List existing sites
- Tap site to view its inspections

**NewInspection.razor** (`/inspection/new/{SiteId}`) - Start new inspection:
- Pre-fills site info
- Inspector name field
- Loads default checklist
- Saves to IndexedDB immediately

**Checklist.razor** (`/inspection/{InspectionId}/checklist`) - Fill out checklist:
- Shows items grouped by category
- Large tap targets for Pass/Fail/N/A
- Optional notes per item
- Auto-saves on each tap (no submit button needed)
- Progress indicator

**Photos.razor** (`/inspection/{InspectionId}/photos`) - Attach photos:
- Camera capture via file input (accept="image/*" capture="environment")
- Show thumbnails of attached photos
- Add caption to each photo
- Photos stored as base64 in IndexedDB

**InspectionDetail.razor** (`/inspection/{InspectionId}`) - View/complete inspection:
- Summary of checklist results
- Notes field
- Photo gallery
- "Complete Inspection" button
- Sync status indicator

### 6. Layout (`SiteInspector.Client/Layout/`)

**MainLayout.razor** - Mobile-first layout:
- Bottom navigation bar (mobile pattern)
- No sidebar (mobile-first)
- Connectivity indicator in header
- Clean, touch-friendly

**MainLayout.razor.css** - Mobile styles

**NavMenu.razor** - Bottom tab bar: Home, Sites, Sync Status

### 7. PWA Support

**In `SiteInspector/wwwroot/`**:
- `manifest.json` - PWA manifest with app name, icons, display: standalone
- `service-worker.js` - Caches app shell for offline use

**In `App.razor`** add:
- `<link rel="manifest" href="manifest.json">`
- Service worker registration script

### 8. Server API Endpoints

**In `SiteInspector/`** add minimal API endpoints for sync:
```csharp
